    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Reference</div>
    <h2>Internal tasks &amp; reminders</h2>
    <p>Beyond the emails, the system also creates the staff and attorney tasks that carry each matter forward — so the right person is prompted at the right moment and nothing depends on memory. These are internal, so there's nothing for you to do here; they're listed so you can see the full picture — each links to its setup in Zoho if you want to look. Tasks tied to a phase that isn't switched on yet will begin firing when that phase goes live.</p>
    <div class="lib-sum">
      <span class="st live"><span class="dot"></span>7 Live</span>
      <span class="st ready"><span class="dot"></span>9 Ready</span>
    </div>
