  <!-- ===== WORKFLOW AUTOMATIONS ===== -->
  <section id="workflows" class="sec">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Reference</div>
    <h2>Workflow automations</h2>
    <p>These are the automation rules working behind the components above — the engine room. There’s nothing to do here; it’s a complete map of what’s running, with each rule linked to its setup in Zoho. A <span class="st live"><span class="dot"></span>Live</span> pill means the rule is switched on; <span class="st ready"><span class="dot"></span>Ready</span> means it’s built and waiting to be switched on, in step with the phases above. A few rules call a custom function, which can’t be linked on its own — those list the function name. Most are background housekeeping; the client-facing ones are the same automations described in each phase.</p>
